content: Wow, that's a lot of characters! It sounds like you have a well-developed cast for your story. The different backgrounds and motivations for each character add depth and complexity to the story, and the division between the Renegades and the Gladiators creates conflict and tension. Additionally, the idea of characters having moles that can eventually be redeemed adds an interesting twist to the plot. Overall, it seems like you have a strong foundation for your story. Good luck with your writing!
